Package com.github.jknack.handlebars.io

Class CompositeTemplateLoader

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.github.jknack.handlebars.io.CompositeTemplateLoader
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    TemplateLoader
    public class CompositeTemplateLoader
extends java.lang.Object
implements TemplateLoader

    Combine two or more TemplateLoader as a single TemplateLoader. TemplateLoaders are executed in the order they are provided.

    Execution is as follows:

    • If a TemplateLoader is able to resolve a TemplateSource, that TemplateSource is considered the response.
    • If a TemplateLoader throws a IOException exception the next TemplateLoader in the chain will be used.
    Since:
    1.0.0
